beer.beer_description:
OK! The concept for this beer is quite simple, take out standard Bling IPA recipe and pimp it to create a Hop Bomb at around 8.50% ALC/VOL
The real challenge was creating an Imperial IPA that reeks of fresh pungent hop aroma, but doesn’t give the impression that it is trying to tear the teeth from jawbone.

We do hope we got it right!
